enable_legacy_metric(25.10)                        enable_legacy_metric(25.10)

Name
       enable_legacy_metric

Syntax
       enable_legacy_metric {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true,  the  old legacy get_metric command is used by the
       tool. By default, it is set  to  false  to  enable  new  usage  of  the
       get_metric command.

Related Information
              * get_metric

